config MERO_X86_THERMAL
	tristate "Mero x86 component thermal initialization"
	depends on X86 && DRM_AMDGPU
	default m
	help
	  Enable the mero thermal zone x86 cpu component driver.
	  The user interface is exposed by generic thermal
	  framework.

	  Say 'Y' if need to enable the mero x86 thermal zone.

config MERO_SOC_THERMAL
	tristate "Mero SOC component thermal initialization"
	depends on X86 && DRM_AMDGPU
	default m
	help
	  Enable the mero thermal zone SOC component driver.
	  The user interface is exposed by generic thermal
	  framework.

	  Say 'Y' if need to enable the mero x86 thermal zone.

